for this airspace docket are based on North American Datum 83. Designations of Class E airspace extending upward from
700 feet or more above the surface are published on Paragraph 6005 of FAA Order 7400.9A dated June 17, 1993, and effective
September 16, 1993, which is incorporated by reference in CFR 71.1 effective September 16, 1993. The Class E airspace
designation listed in this document would be published subsequently in the Order. 
