of American National Standard Requirements for Protective Headwear for Industrial Workers, ANSI Z89.1&hyph;1986.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) Protective hats previously worn shall be cleaned and disinfected before issuance by the employer to another employee.

