For the last item in this section of Appendix I, EPA is proposing to move existing item L.7.d. to L.8.e. This item describes
revising the final operating conditions to reflect the results of the trial burn. Changes in the final permit should
reflect the operating conditions under which the facility met the required performance standards during the trial
